OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,FUS President Donald Trump says he has
OL,8,Fagreed to suspend the "destructive
OL,9,Fforce" he had threatened against Iran.
OL,11,FPosting on Truth Social, Trump said he
OL,12,Fwas holding off on his threatened
OL,13,Fattacks on Iranian bridges, power
OL,14,Fplants and other civilian targets,
OL,15,Fsubject to Tehran agreeing to a two-
OL,16,Fweek ceasefire and reopening of the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz, the pivotal waterway
OL,18,Fthrough which a fifth of the world's
OL,19,Foil is transported during peacetime.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@FO]
