OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,FHe also said Iran has proposed a
OL,8,F"workable" ten-point peace plan that
OL,9,Fcould help end the war.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
