FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,FHe wrote: "Based on conversations with
OL,8,FPrime Minister Shehbaz Sharif and
OL,9,FField Marshal Asim Munir, of Pakistan,
OL,10,Fand wherein they requested that I hold
OL,11,Foff the destructive force being sent
OL,12,Ftonight to Iran, and subject to the
OL,13,FIslamic Republic of Iran agreeing to
OL,14,Fthe COMPLETE, IMMEDIATE, and SAFE
OL,15,FOPENING of the Strait of Hormuz, I
OL,16,Fagree to suspend the bombing and
OL,17,Fattack of Iran for a period of two
OL,18,Fweeks.
OL,20,F"This will be a double sided CEASEFIRE!
OL,26,@oD@KOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,F"The reason for doing so is that we
OL,8,Fhave already met and exceeded all
OL,9,FMilitary objectives, and are very far
OL,10,Falong with a definitive Agreement
OL,11,Fconcerning Longterm PEACE with Iran,
OL,12,Fand PEACE in the Middle East.
OL,14,F"We received a 10 point proposal from
OL,15,FIran, and believe it is a workable
OL,16,Fbasis on which to negotiate. Almost
OL,17,Fall of the various points of past
OL,18,Fcontention have been agreed to between
OL,19,Fthe United States and Iran, but a two
OL,20,Fweek period will allow the Agreement
OL,21,Fto be finalized and consummated.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
