PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,F"On behalf of the United States of
OL,8,FAmerica, as President, and also
OL,9,Frepresenting the Countries of the
OL,10,FMiddle East, it is an Honor to have
OL,11,Fthis Longterm problem close to
OL,12,Fresolution."
OL,14,FIran's Supreme National Security
OL,15,FCouncil has since said it has accepted
OL,16,Fa two-week ceasefire.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@LO]
