PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,FForeign minister Abbas Araghchi also
OL,8,Fsaid passage through the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz would be allowed for the next
OL,10,Ftwo weeks under Iranian military
OL,11,Fmanagement.
OL,13,FIn a statement on behalf of the
OL,14,FSupreme National Security Council, he
OL,15,Fsaid: "If attacks against Iran are
OL,16,Fhalted, our Powerful Armed Forces will
OL,17,Fcease their defensive operations.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
