OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1775642746
OL,3,CTrump agrees to two-week ceasefire
OL,4,Cwith Iran if Strait of Hormuz is
OL,5,Creopened
OL,7,F"For a period of two weeks, safe
OL,8,Fpassage through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,9,Fwill be possible via coordination with
OL,10,FIran's Armed Forces and with due
OL,11,Fconsideration of technical
OL,12,Flimitations."
